{"tid":187494,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲黎緊會去俄羅斯","createTime":"2017-04-05T04:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T15:06:15.000Z","uid":39753,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5309a414725ca8c238c0587dd238a9b126099b1","tid":187494,"uid":39753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T04:26:17.000Z","msg":"想去俄羅斯玩好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住6月sem break去玩返兩個禮拜<br />\n莫斯科+金環+聖彼得堡<br />\n原本預左治安都唔會好得去邊<br />\n點知而家仲出埋事<br />\n驚到瀨屎但係又想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家心大心細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763f4323257aaa39e923df7feeca5cdc0f29dc05","tid":187494,"uid":4516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T04:38:36.000Z","msg":"下星期去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db30388a032ec9ec56f65fa19e541fd029ca3fc0","tid":187494,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T04:46:12.000Z","msg":"好撚危險，千祈唔好去。<br />\n<br />\n旺角騷亂後，我成年都冇出過旺角。<br />\n<br />\n嚟梗應該連朗豪坊都唔會去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893da923a04ce84edbfce1e0e2f880e69eaace27","tid":187494,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"仲有<br />\n<br />\n印尼排華後，真係唔敢去印尼。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓人質事件後，都唔敢去菲律賓。<br />\n<br />\n嚟梗都唔敢去旅行，真係唔知出發前當地會唔會有恐襲發生。<br />\n<br />\n早一日發生，都唔知去唔去好！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5abcac499430cc6ab8eaf6cd71feaa7b956d75c9","tid":187494,"uid":1666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T06:04:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚危險，千祈唔好去。<br />\n<br />\n旺角騷亂後，我成年都冇出過旺角。<br />\n<br />\n嚟梗應該連朗豪坊都唔會去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blo